4. Aguero M, Fernandez-Pinero J, Buitrago D, Sanchez A, Elizalde M, San Miguel E, et al.: Bagaza virus in partridges and pheasants, Spain, 2010. Emerg Infect Dis. 2011; 17(8): 1498-1501. DOI: 10.3201/eid1708.110077.
